@SBAgov recently released more information about how small businesses participating in the Paycheck Protection Program can qualify for loan forgiveness.

This forgiveness application doesn’t provide all the answers, but it’s a start. You can find it here: 
https://t.co/2tgjmrUhUb

You've probably heard that Governor Mills issued a stay-at-home order yesterday.

Folks have a lot of questions about the order and what it means for them. There are some good answers from 
@KJ_Online here: https://t.co/owbfFcUBkz 1/

We all need to be making changes to our daily lives right now, and that starts with knowing what to do and why we’re doing it. 

@bangordailynews has a good primer on social distancing, self-quarantine, and self-isolation here:
https://t.co/PIe1Lt9ql1

